Alias      Myanti-D0   anti-D0
Alias      MyD0        D0
ChargeConj MyD0        Myanti-D0
Alias MyD*0 D*0
Alias Myanti-D*0 anti-D*0
ChargeConj MyD*0 Myanti-D*0
Alias Mypi0 pi0
##
Decay B-sig
  1.000     MyD*0  pi-               SVS;
Enddecay
CDecay B+sig
#
Decay MyD*0
1.    MyD0  Mypi0                       VSS;
Enddecay
CDecay Myanti-D*0

#
Decay MyD0
  1.000     K-  pi+        PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay Myanti-D0
#
Decay Mypi0
1.0000  gamma gamma                         PHSP;
Enddecay
